<h6 data-zesty-id="content:text:1:71">The Salvation Army Honor Cards</h6>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:2:6"><strong>Honor Someone You Love.&nbsp; Help Someone In Need.</strong></p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:3:73">This Christmas season, you can give a gift that warms more than one heart.</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:4:77">
	When you purchase a <strong>Salvation Army Honor Card</strong>, you’re not only celebrating someone special—you’re helping provide <strong>food, shelter, and care</strong> for neighbors in need right here in Greater Winston-Salem.
</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:5:49">
	Each <strong>hand-painted greeting card</strong> is created by a local artist and printed as a beautiful 7" × 5" folded Christmas card with a heartfelt message inside. It’s a simple yet meaningful way to share hope and love during the Christmas season.
</p>
<div class="my-4" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-md:6:18"></div>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:7:51">
	<b>How It Works</b>
</p>
<ol data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:8:68">
	<li><strong>Download and complete the order form </strong>below.</li>
	<li>Email your form to:&nbsp;catherine.snipes@uss.salvationarmy.org</li>
</ol>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:9:9"></div>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:10:24">
	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; or mail it to:
</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:11:28"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;The Salvation Army of Greater Winston-Salem</strong></p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:12:96">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;PO Box 1205</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:13:11">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Winston-Salem, NC 27102</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:14:86">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3. We’ll take care of the rest—sending your Honor Cards to you or directly to your recipients.</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:15:7"><strong>Suggested Donation: $10 per card</strong></p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:16:21">
	Every card helps bring comfort, meals, and shelter to struggling families in our community.
</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:17:37"><strong>Questions?</strong></p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:18:43">Contact <strong>Cathy Snipes</strong> at <a href="mailto:catherine.snipes@uss.salvationarmy.org">catherine.snipes@uss.salvationarmy.org</a></p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:19:38"></div>
<p data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:20:10">
	<span style="color:#ffffff;"><a href="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/10d5f235-6982-48ca-ae81-5cac99b46ace_Christmas+Honor+Card+Order+Form.pdf" class="btn btn-secondary gap-1 mt-2">Download Honor Card Order Form</a></span>
</p>
